      • getFilledObjectRepList

        public static 
Phase2.ObjectRepList 
getFilledObjectRepList(Phase2.ObjectRepList  unfilled)
        initializes a ObjectRepList with hardcoded Object, String and Class data fills ObjectRepList using unfilled list with fill method that also sets parents of Objects resolves VTable structure for each object using inheritance relationship proces inherited fields for data layout for each object using inheritance relationship removes object with main method as this does not need to be processed removes Object, String and Class at the last step as these are not needed anymore
        Parameters:
        unfilled - unprocessed ObjectRepList from visitor
        Returns:
        filled ObjectRepList of resolved ctable and data layouts for each object

      • fill

        public static 
Phase2.ObjectRepList 
fill(Phase2.ObjectRepList  filled,
     Phase2.ObjectRepList  unfilled)
        Helper method for getFilledObjectRepList that fills up the ObjectRep structure based on its inheritance heirarchy, ensuring that if B inherits A, then B occurs further down on the ObjectRepList, it also adds pointers to relevant parents i.e. B now points to A and A points to Object
        Parameters:
        filled - ObjectRepList with just Object, String and Class
        unfilled - ObjectRepList of visitor processed Objects
        Returns:
        filled ObjectRepList with proper inheritance hierarchy
